<bug>
	<id>5435</id>
	<title>DOCKER_OPTS - multiple DNS</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">A user can specify multiple dns options in the /etc/defaults/docker file such as:
`DOCKER_OPTS="--dns 8.8.8.8 --dns 192.168.1.2 -e lxc"`
However only the first dns option will be used.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
